1
00:00:18,410 --> 00:00:21,420
♪Wearing peach blossom makeup,
I boil tea over the stove♪

2
00:00:23,060 --> 00:00:25,780
♪With a pure heart,
I embroider the brocade of time♪

3
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,380
♪On the short paper,
affection flows in the silent moonlight♪

4
00:00:31,820 --> 00:00:34,940
♪I only wish that by my side,
is my love♪

5
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:39,940
♪Cool autumn wind blowing,
I gaze far leaning against the railing♪

6
00:00:41,620 --> 00:00:44,460
♪Sunset glow over the green hill,
in formation wild geese are flying♪

7
00:00:45,940 --> 00:00:50,020
♪Covering a thousand miles on horseback,
for whom is he longing♪

8
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:53,620
♪He returned home in dreams♪

9
00:00:54,060 --> 00:00:57,820
♪I will never forget
that you held my hands♪

10
00:00:58,740 --> 00:01:02,540
♪In your warm palms
and we braved winds and waves♪

11
00:01:03,380 --> 00:01:07,980
♪Unexpectedly, after we traveled so far
and turned grey-haired♪

12
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:11,660
♪I am still by your side♪

13
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:16,500
♪Hearts burning,
we look into each other's eyes♪

14
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:21,140
♪Feelings overflowing,
they don't need to be hided♪

15
00:01:21,820 --> 00:01:26,420
♪No matter how time passes
and life changes♪

16
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:30,860
♪Together, we will grow old♪

17
00:01:32,420 --> 00:01:36,100
=The Sword and the Brocade=

18
00:01:36,980 --> 00:01:39,260
=Episode 30=

19
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:45,880
Mr. Ou?

20
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:48,160
It's them.

21
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,160
Madam Xu?

22
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:53,520
Young Master.

23
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,200
Young Master. Young Master.

24
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:56,440
It's Madam Xu.

25
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:09,080
Mr. Ou, what brought you here?

26
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,160
Master Jian and I

27
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,400
heard Marquis Yongping had an accident,

28
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,240
and you were expelled by Xu family.

29
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,360
I was quite worried,

30
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,320
so I came here and check on you.

31
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:18,120
I'm fine. No need to worry.

32
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,400
I saw what happened earlier.

33
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,800
How can I believe that you are fine?

34
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,400
Look at your hands.

35
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,120
You are so passionate about embroidery.

36
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,680
You shouldn't ruin your hands

37
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:34,960
on a tough job like that.

38
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:37,160
Even if something bad happens
to Marquis Yongping,

39
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,760
it's not your fault.

40
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:40,920
They shouldn't blame you.

41
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,760
I misunderstood His Lordship

42
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:45,560
and hurt his feelings.

43
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:47,840
I feel sorry for what I did to him.

44
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:49,120
I should be punished.

45
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,320
Misunderstood?

46
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,640
Can you be sure

47
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:55,000
that you really misunderstood him?

48
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:59,080
Come to think of it,

49
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,160
the evidence

50
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,040
all led me to suspect His Lordship.

51
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,200
It's my fault that I was being impulsive

52
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,480
and wasn't thinking straight,

53
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:07,720
having my mind clouded by doubts.

54
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,400
Now that I think about it again,

55
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,360
it must be someone
who misled me on purpose.

56
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,880
Shiyi, are you saying that

57
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,520
because I'm one of the Ou family?

58
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,400
You suspect that I gave you

59
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:22,440
all the clues on purpose

60
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,680
in order to make you
hate Marquis Yongping?

61
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,960
I'm not suspecting you.

62
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:28,680
It's just that the Ou family

63
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:31,000
and the Xu family have held a grudge
against each other for long.

64
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,640
I don't want you

65
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,240
to help me anymore.

66
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,760
Mr. Ou, please leave.

67
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,320
Too many eyes are watching.

68
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,880
If people see you are here,

69
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:42,640
they'll misunderstand us again.

70
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,240
I understand.

71
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:49,000
Take good care of yourself.

72
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:51,840
Thank you, Mr. Ou.

73
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,680
Amber.

74
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:05,920
Mr. Ou's hand is hurt.

75
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,440
Go get some medicine for him.

76
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,520
Yes, Your Ladyship.

77
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,440
Mr. Ou,

78
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,880
thank you for traveling a long way here

79
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:23,320
to help us.

80
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,240
But there's something

81
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,160
I have to say to you.

82
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,640
His Lordship's whereabouts is unknown.

83
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,440
You'd better leave here

84
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,440
in case of any trouble.

85
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,200
If the Xu family finds out that you

86
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,840
and Her Ladyship still
talk to each other,

87
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,200
they'll blame you

88
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,240
for His Lordship's

89
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,440
accident for sure.

90
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,120
I'm not afraid since
I've done nothing wrong.

91
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,360
What matters the most right now

92
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,760
is Shiyi's safety.

93
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:49,520
How can I leave knowing

94
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,440
that she's suffering here?

95
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,440
But what if...

96
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,120
Don't worry.

97
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,920
I will be careful.

98
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,840
I won't let the Xu family find out,

99
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:00,960
and I won't put Shiyi in trouble.

100
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,720
Mr. Ou, you are from a wealthy family.

101
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:06,120
Why do you have to hide
in this shabby place

102
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:08,080
and make yourself suffer?

103
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,840
There aren't so many reasons.

104
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:17,080
I'm doing this because I want to.

105
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,040
Neat stitches

106
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:45,720
layered with bright colors.

107
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,600
Obviously, it's

108
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:48,720
Shiyi's work.

109
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,600
Mr. Ou, good eye.

110
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,560
Her Ladyship made
this Bodhisattva's portrait

111
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,920
to pray safety for His Lordship.

112
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,120
But I see her working hard

113
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,520
all day long.

114
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:08,080
How could she still have time for this?

115
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,200
Her Ladyship

116
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,920
sacrificed her sleeping time for it.

117
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:14,280
We couldn't stop her
no matter how hard we tried.

118
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,560
Mr. Ou, look.

119
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:21,720
The stitches here

120
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,960
were originally made

121
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,960
of black silk thread.

122
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,040
But

123
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:25,960
we ran out of

124
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,040
black silk thread,

125
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,280
so Her Ladyship

126
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,000
thought of using

127
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,720
her hair instead.

128
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,120
To our surprise,

129
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:33,680
it turned out to be even
better than silk thread.

130
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,120
Because of that,

131
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:37,160
we finally saw Her Ladyship smile.

132
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,120
Amber,

133
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,320
you and Dongqing

134
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,720
have got to take good care of her.

135
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,640
She is so passionate about embroidery

136
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,120
and she's very gifted.

137
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,640
If her hands get hurt,

138
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:51,320
she'll never be able to do that again.

139
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,440
Mr. Ou, no worries.

140
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,120
Dongqing and I

141
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,840
will certainly take good
care of Her Ladyship.

142
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,720
You also need to take
good care of yourselves.

143
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,720
Mr. Ou, don't just think of us.

144
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,640
You should take care
of yourself as well.

145
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:08,600
You need to change medicine regularly.

146
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:11,920
Thank you.

147
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:45,200
Who are you?

148
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,160
Why do you want to kill me?

149
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:48,600
Stop.

150
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:50,120
Stop.

151
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,960
Guards, take him.

152
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,520
Freeze.

153
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:58,720
Don't move.

154
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:03,880
Oh,

155
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,040
it's you.

156
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,240
Take him away.

157
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:07,600
-Move.
-Hurry.

158
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,280
Move.

159
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:11,800
Your Ladyship, sorry about that.

160
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,920
Chief steward, thank you for saving me.

161
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,720
I should thank you, Your Ladyship.

162
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:16,640
If it hadn't been for you,

163
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:17,480
I wouldn't have been able

164
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,920
to catch this ungrateful rascal.

165
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,240
What?

166
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:26,000
Someone in the farm
attempted to kill you?

167
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,080
Your Ladyship.

168
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:30,840
Are you out of your mind?

169
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,670
Chief steward,

170
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:34,520
no matter what,

171
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:36,600
I'm still Marquis Yongping's wife,

172
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,240
the matron of Xu family.

173
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:41,400
If anything happens

174
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:42,760
to me here,

175
00:08:42,910 --> 00:08:44,880
you'll be held accountable for it.

176
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:51,520
So, what are you going to do,
Your Ladyship?

177
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,240
Move.

178
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,120
How come you are still here?

179
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,120
Antai said

180
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,200
that someone just attacked you.

181
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,400
Shiyi,

182
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:17,120
what happened to you exactly?

183
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,400
I'm fine.

184
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,520
You don't need to worry.

185
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:20,080
No.

186
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,680
If you don't tell me,

187
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,440
I won't leave here whatsoever.

188
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:36,760
A few days ago,

189
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:38,480
someone went through my stuff

190
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:40,160
and pushed me into a well,

191
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:42,120
but nothing was stolen,

192
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:43,920
which means he wasn't going after money.

193
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:44,920
So,

194
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:46,760
just now, I was trying to lure him out.

195
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,240
I didn't expect

196
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,040
that he is the assistant steward.

197
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,480
The assistant steward?

198
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,880
He didn't go after money,

199
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:57,840
and he has nothing against you.

200
00:09:59,080 --> 00:09:59,960
Think again.

201
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:01,280
Is there anything

202
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,680
valuable among

203
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:03,680
your belongings?

204
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,520
The embroidery cloth.

205
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:12,040
Was he trying to steal
my embroidery cloth?

206
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:14,320
Maybe the murderer
who killed your mother

207
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,440
started to make a move on you.

208
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,920
It's possible.

209
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,320
But like you said,

210
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,440
the assistant steward
has nothing against me.

211
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,800
And he didn't go after my money.

212
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:29,040
So it only means

213
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,840
that someone asked him to do it.

214
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,320
Now that he's caught by you,

215
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:34,920
the person who's behind this

216
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:36,200
may not give up easily.

217
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:38,840
He may even plan on killing you.

218
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:39,760
No.

219
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,520
You must leave here right now.

220
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:43,600
I finally found some leads.

221
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:44,600
I won't leave.

222
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:45,920
Alright.

223
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,360
I've told you what happened.

224
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,360
You can leave now.

225
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:50,440
I have the chief steward
to help me here.

226
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:51,520
You need not to worry.

227
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,840
The chief steward?

228
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,880
Don't you remember how he treated you?

229
00:10:58,220 --> 00:11:06,380
(Grain)

230
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:29,320
Wang Jinzhong.

231
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:31,280
How dare you

232
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:33,440
attempt to kill Her Ladyship?

233
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,720
We have nothing against each other.

234
00:11:36,880 --> 00:11:38,280
Why did you try to kill me?

235
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:40,200
Who asked you to do it?

236
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,280
Wang Jinzhong.

237
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:48,680
Have you thought

238
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,080
about your current situation?

239
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:52,040
You failed your mission,

240
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,560
so you've been disavowed.

241
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,040
Who would care about

242
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,720
a disavowed person's life?

243
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,800
At the moment,

244
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:05,080
only the Xu family can protect you.

245
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:06,360
As long as you tell me

246
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:07,680
who's behind this,

247
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:09,640
the Xu family will
guarantee your safety.

248
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:14,680
But you can't even protect yourself,

249
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,320
how could you make sure

250
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,360
that the Xu family can protect me?

251
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:21,760
Whoever wants to kill me

252
00:12:21,920 --> 00:12:23,400
will surely do harm to Xu family.

253
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:25,520
Therefore, the Xu family
won't sit back and watch.

254
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,920
Think carefully.

255
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,240
This is

256
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:37,120
your only chance to stay alive.

257
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:38,360
Say it.

258
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:40,360
Who asked you to do it?

259
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:41,960
Alright. Alright.

260
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:43,080
I'll say it.

261
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,280
I'll say it.

262
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,240
Actually...

263
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:48,840
Actually the one who wants
to kill Her Ladyship is...

264
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,720
Screw you.

265
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:54,440
Stop.

266
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,680
You won't let me off even if I tell you.

267
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,720
-Hurry.
-Get him.

268
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,320
Kill all of them.

269
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:15,400
Protect Her Ladyship.

270
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:41,240
Shiyi, are you alright?

271
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,080
Mr. Ou.

272
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,720
It's dangerous here. Run.

273
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:44,480
Watch out.

274
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,200
Mr. Ou.

275
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:49,720
Run.

