289
00:15:37,040 --> 00:15:38,680
Has your wound healed?

290
00:15:40,880 --> 00:15:41,800
Almost.

291
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:59,840
They all said that the fire killed you.

292
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:05,160
But I just didn't believe it.

293
00:16:15,760 --> 00:16:17,400
When I was ordered to go to Shandong,

294
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:22,080
you were misled into suspecting me.

295
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:24,800
So I thought that the Shandong trip

296
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,960
could also be part of their plan.

297
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:30,920
So I kept alert on my way.

298
00:16:32,280 --> 00:16:33,120
Not long after,

299
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,400
I found that

300
00:16:35,520 --> 00:16:36,920
some people were sneaking around

301
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,320
and waited to make a move.

302
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:40,240
So you deliberately

303
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:41,720
set the inn on fire

304
00:16:42,120 --> 00:16:44,320
to lure out those people?

305
00:16:49,400 --> 00:16:50,600
Although I suspected that they

306
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,920
were sent by Ou family,

307
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:55,400
I wasn't quite sure

308
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:58,080
until the Ou family

309
00:16:58,200 --> 00:17:00,120
thought that I was killed by the fire

310
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,520
and started their evildoings
without any scruple.

311
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:04,480
They even

312
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,760
made me a scapegoat for

313
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:07,960
the embezzlement they did in Shandong.

314
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:10,200
After it's confirmed,

315
00:17:10,590 --> 00:17:11,680
I got back on them

316
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:14,000
without they preparing for it.

317
00:17:15,110 --> 00:17:16,560
In order to make them believe

318
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:18,350
that you were killed by the fire,

319
00:17:19,110 --> 00:17:21,520
the fire must've been very fierce.

320
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:24,350
You were badly injured.

321
00:17:26,070 --> 00:17:27,590
It must have been quite difficult

322
00:17:28,310 --> 00:17:29,840
for you to escape.

323
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:53,120
How did you know I was here?

324
00:17:55,120 --> 00:17:56,280
On my way back,

325
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:58,600
I bumped into Wan Daxian

326
00:17:59,400 --> 00:18:00,880
and learned that Mother was mad at you,

327
00:18:01,320 --> 00:18:02,280
so I rushed here.

328
00:18:05,320 --> 00:18:06,720
Actually, you could've showed

329
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:08,400
them the Divorce Agreement

330
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,920
and left Xu family.

331
00:18:12,320 --> 00:18:13,760
Why did you

332
00:18:14,120 --> 00:18:15,120
come here and make

333
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:16,560
yourself suffer?

334
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:19,480
How could I just take the

335
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:21,360
Divorce Agreement and leave?

336
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,760
I wouldn't leave.

337
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:26,720
I was still waiting for you
to come back.

338
00:18:45,920 --> 00:18:47,160
Who are those people

339
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:48,560
in black?

340
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:51,240
What happened here?

341
00:18:55,040 --> 00:18:56,800
I'm not sure

342
00:18:57,520 --> 00:18:59,440
who those people in black are.

343
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:01,480
But the assistant steward here

344
00:19:01,600 --> 00:19:02,840
has been bought off

345
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:04,800
and attempted to kill me.

346
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:07,280
The chief steward caught him.

347
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:09,400
When we were just trying to
find out who's behind this,

348
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:12,520
he was shot to death by an arrow.

349
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:14,760
So you are sure

350
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,040
that those people were here for you.

351
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,920
They wanted to kill you.

352
00:19:26,600 --> 00:19:27,840
Then what about Ou Yanxing?

353
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:30,480
What is he doing here?

354
00:19:31,120 --> 00:19:33,880
Master Jian was worried about me,

355
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,160
so she asked Ou Yanxing

356
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:37,080
to come here and check on me.

357
00:19:41,360 --> 00:19:42,440
By the way, My Lord,

358
00:19:42,840 --> 00:19:44,760
do you still remember that coroner,

359
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:46,120
the one who led me

360
00:19:46,320 --> 00:19:47,880
into suspecting you?

361
00:19:48,280 --> 00:19:51,040
He was actually found by Ou Yanxing.

362
00:19:51,760 --> 00:19:53,480
But I know Ou Yanxing very well.

363
00:19:53,640 --> 00:19:55,040
He wouldn't do such thing.

364
00:19:55,320 --> 00:19:56,480
So I suspect

365
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:57,800
that he was used.

366
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,840
And the people who are able

367
00:19:59,840 --> 00:20:00,680
to use him without him knowing it

368
00:20:01,560 --> 00:20:03,200
can only be the Ou family.

369
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:05,720
So you think

370
00:20:06,160 --> 00:20:07,760
it's the Ou family who killed

371
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:09,000
your mother?

372
00:20:10,840 --> 00:20:12,280
It's just a conjecture.

373
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:34,760
Thank you

374
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:36,400
for saving my wife

375
00:20:36,840 --> 00:20:37,680
when her life was in danger.

376
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:39,560
Marquis Yongping,

377
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:41,800
to be honest,

378
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:43,920
the coroner who misled Madam Xu

379
00:20:44,040 --> 00:20:44,920
was found by me.

380
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:47,480
I made a careless mistake.

381
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:50,120
Please don't misunderstand Madam Xu.

382
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:52,760
I trust my wife,

383
00:20:53,120 --> 00:20:54,760
but I don't trust the Ou family.

384
00:20:57,840 --> 00:20:59,040
You can misunderstand me,

385
00:21:00,280 --> 00:21:01,240
but please try to understand

386
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,640
Madam Xu's anxiety

387
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:05,040
for the truth.

388
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:07,520
It's between me and my wife.

389
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,760
It's none of anybody else's business.

390
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:15,480
Mr. Ou,

391
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:16,680
thank you for

392
00:21:16,840 --> 00:21:18,200
taking care of me these days.

393
00:21:18,600 --> 00:21:20,720
His Lordship and I will go home now.

394
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:45,000
It's been so many days.

395
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:47,760
Why is there still

396
00:21:48,840 --> 00:21:51,880
no news from Shandong?

397
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:55,160
Mother, no news

398
00:21:55,320 --> 00:21:57,040
is unnecessarily a bad thing.

399
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:04,000
Great Madam.

400
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:05,280
Good news.

401
00:22:05,560 --> 00:22:07,200
His Lordship sent a message,

402
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:08,280
saying he's fine

403
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,880
and he'll be home soon.

404
00:22:15,720 --> 00:22:16,960
Lingyi is alive.

405
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:18,240
That's so great.

406
00:22:18,520 --> 00:22:19,280
I just knew

407
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:20,480
that a tough man like him

408
00:22:20,600 --> 00:22:21,880
wouldn't die easily.

409
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:23,120
Steward Bai,

410
00:22:23,360 --> 00:22:24,480
prepare some good wine.

411
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:25,760
I'll have a drink tonight

412
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:27,080
to celebrate.

413
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:28,080
Yes.

414
00:22:28,560 --> 00:22:29,480
That's great.

415
00:22:30,120 --> 00:22:30,760
Mother,

416
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:32,800
now we can finally be relieved.

417
00:22:41,120 --> 00:22:42,280
Danyang.

418
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:43,320
Master Lingkuan.

419
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,240
Danyang.

420
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,040
Danyang.

421
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:47,480
Danyang.

422
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:49,440
Fiftth Madam is asleep already,
Master Lingkuan.

423
00:22:49,600 --> 00:22:50,680
Asleep?

424
00:22:51,520 --> 00:22:53,080
Then I won't wake her up.

425
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:54,720
Help me...

426
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:56,920
Help me to the East Chamber to sleep.

427
00:22:57,040 --> 00:22:58,080
Yes.

428
00:22:58,240 --> 00:22:59,200
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

