00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:19,520
Water.

431
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:22,080
Water.

432
00:23:32,040 --> 00:23:33,360
Xiaolan?

433
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:35,280
What are you doing here?

434
00:23:41,280 --> 00:23:42,320
It's all my fault.

435
00:23:42,600 --> 00:23:44,080
I was confused.

436
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:45,320
Danyang.

437
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:46,760
You can hit me. You can yell at me.

438
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:48,960
But please don't ignore me.

439
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:03,880
It's alright.

440
00:24:04,600 --> 00:24:06,640
It's not a big deal.

441
00:24:07,320 --> 00:24:09,560
Lingkuan, you don't have
to be like this.

442
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:12,520
Help Lingkuan to get up.

443
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:15,600
If others see this,

444
00:24:16,080 --> 00:24:18,120
they'll laugh at us.

445
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:20,120
-Master Lingkuan.
-Danyang.

446
00:24:20,560 --> 00:24:21,800
Please trust me.

447
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:24,240
You are the only one I love

448
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:26,320
and I'll love you forever.

449
00:24:27,120 --> 00:24:28,040
Last night

450
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:30,120
it was just a misunderstanding.

451
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:31,800
That's right, Madam.

452
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:33,720
Last night

453
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:35,640
Master Lingkuan was drunk.

454
00:24:35,760 --> 00:24:37,760
He mistook me for you.

455
00:24:38,120 --> 00:24:39,280
That's why...

456
00:24:39,760 --> 00:24:41,480
Madam, I'm willing to be punished.

457
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:45,560
It's okay.

458
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:47,400
Look how scared you are.

459
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:49,000
Just get up.

460
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:51,600
Since you've slept

461
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:53,080
with Lingkuan,

462
00:24:53,520 --> 00:24:54,640
how can I

463
00:24:54,760 --> 00:24:56,000
punish you?

464
00:24:57,240 --> 00:24:59,240
I will not punish you, instead,

465
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:02,720
I'll make you a concubine.

466
00:25:03,760 --> 00:25:05,400
From now on,

467
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:08,480
you will serve Lingkuan
together with me.

468
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:11,240
Madam, thank you.

469
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,200
By the way,

470
00:25:14,840 --> 00:25:17,200
you and Xiaodie have
been friends for years.

471
00:25:18,240 --> 00:25:20,360
You may not be used to another maid.

472
00:25:20,520 --> 00:25:21,840
I'll let Xiaodie

473
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:23,560
be your maid. How's that?

474
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:29,200
Yes, Madam.

475
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:32,120
Lingkuan,

476
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,880
do you think my arrangement

477
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,480
is proper?

478
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:38,680
I swear.

479
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:40,120
I won't do such

480
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:41,760
ridiculous thing ever again.

481
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:44,840
Master Lingkuan,

482
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:45,840
His Lordship is back.

483
00:25:45,960 --> 00:25:47,280
He's arrived at the front gate.

484
00:25:49,440 --> 00:25:51,480
Lingkuan, go and welcome His Lordship.

485
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:53,000
It's inconvenient for me to walk.

486
00:25:53,400 --> 00:25:55,000
I'll just stay here.

487
00:25:57,680 --> 00:26:00,320
Then take a good rest.

488
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:14,640
You may leave now.

489
00:26:15,240 --> 00:26:17,120
Yes, Madam.

490
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:25,640
Madam,

491
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:27,600
why did you do that?

492
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:29,320
If you are upset,

493
00:26:29,560 --> 00:26:31,760
just send Xiaolan away.

494
00:26:34,840 --> 00:26:36,440
Send this Xiaolan away,

495
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:39,720
there may come another Xiaolan.

496
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:43,040
Besides, Jie's matter

497
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:44,760
caused such a chaos last time.

498
00:26:45,520 --> 00:26:46,680
My father was quite angry

499
00:26:46,800 --> 00:26:47,600
with Lingkuan.

500
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:50,520
If he knows about this,

501
00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:53,200
he won't let Lingkuan off easily,

502
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:55,160
which will hurt

503
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:56,760
my relationship with Lingkuan.

504
00:26:58,080 --> 00:26:59,880
And people will criticize me

505
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:01,680
for being jealous.

506
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:05,720
In that case,

507
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:09,040
I'll put myself and my baby

508
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:12,080
in a difficult position.

509
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:14,240
Madam, you've become

510
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:16,000
so sensible.

511
00:27:16,360 --> 00:27:17,680
It actually makes

512
00:27:18,320 --> 00:27:20,320
me feel even sadder.

513
00:27:21,320 --> 00:27:23,280
Nanny Shi, you told me

514
00:27:23,800 --> 00:27:25,760
that I'll be a mother soon;

515
00:27:26,400 --> 00:27:28,200
I can't be that willful anymore.

516
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:34,600
My Lord, you are back.

517
00:27:41,120 --> 00:27:41,800
Mother.

518
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:44,240
My son, rise.

519
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:45,960
Please rise.

520
00:27:49,400 --> 00:27:50,600
My son.

521
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:54,320
I've been looking forward
to your return.

522
00:27:55,760 --> 00:27:57,040
Do you know that?

523
00:27:57,720 --> 00:27:59,680
You are the protector

524
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:03,240
and the pillar of Xu family.

525
00:28:04,520 --> 00:28:06,880
I can't live without you.

526
00:28:09,760 --> 00:28:10,840
Mother, it's my fault.

527
00:28:11,400 --> 00:28:13,360
I'm sorry that I made you worried.

528
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:15,200
Mother,

529
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:16,840
it's a happy thing
that His Lordship is back.

530
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:18,320
He had a long journey.

531
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:19,680
Let's go inside first.

532
00:28:20,120 --> 00:28:21,800
Okay. Go inside.

533
00:28:21,920 --> 00:28:23,440
Let's go inside.

534
00:28:23,520 --> 00:28:23,880
Mother.

535
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:26,200
Wait a moment.

536
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:35,320
Shiyi?

537
00:28:52,240 --> 00:28:53,760
Shiyi.

538
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:55,040
Mother.

539
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:58,360
Why did you bring her back?

540
00:28:58,920 --> 00:29:01,160
Shiyi is my wife.

541
00:29:01,840 --> 00:29:03,200
Of course I'll take her back.

542
00:29:03,400 --> 00:29:05,000
I won't allow it.

543
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:07,440
This woman

544
00:29:07,640 --> 00:29:09,560
attempted to hurt her husband.

545
00:29:09,800 --> 00:29:10,760
I won't allow her

546
00:29:10,840 --> 00:29:12,720
to step into our Xu family.

547
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:15,040
Mother, you misunderstood.

548
00:29:15,560 --> 00:29:17,040
It's not like what you think.

549
00:29:17,800 --> 00:29:18,960
There are too many people passing by.

550
00:29:19,080 --> 00:29:19,840
Let's go in first.

551
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:21,240
I'll explain it to you.

552
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:48,840
I've heard what you said.

553
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:53,000
But it's a fact that Shiyi stabbed you.

554
00:29:53,760 --> 00:29:55,120
I was going to deal with her

555
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:58,320
after you are back.

556
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,640
But this woman

557
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:03,240
actually dared hurt her own husband.

558
00:30:03,360 --> 00:30:05,040
Our Xu family has no place

559
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:07,080
for such a sinful person.

560
00:30:08,040 --> 00:30:08,920
Mother,

561
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:10,560
it's all my fault.

562
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:11,880
-I...
-Mother,

563
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:13,360
it's just a misunderstanding.

564
00:30:15,320 --> 00:30:16,360
I made myself hurt

565
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:17,720
on purpose.

566
00:30:18,200 --> 00:30:18,920
And the wound wasn't

567
00:30:19,040 --> 00:30:20,240
as serious as you thought.

568
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:21,400
It was all

569
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:23,320
an act to fool the Ou family.

570
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:25,440
To help me

